{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-4a5b-8c9d-0e1f2a3b4c5d",
    "name": "RBPO Backend",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": "1) Выполните **Login as ADMIN** — токен сохранится в accessToken.\n2) **Signatures**: сначала **Create signature** — в ответе будет id, он сохранится в signatureId. После этого работают Update, Delete, Get by IDs, Get history, Get audit.\n3) **Signatures files** (задание 6): только ADMIN — загрузка файла в MinIO и presigned URL; нужен запущенный MinIO (`docker compose up`).\n4) **Signatures binary**: после логина USER/ADMIN — бинарная выгрузка multipart.\n5) baseUrl по умолчанию http://localhost:8081."
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8081" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "username", "value": "testuser" },
    { "key": "password", "value": "Test123!@#" },
    { "key": "activationKey", "value": "" },
    { "key": "deviceMac", "value": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:01" },
    { "key": "productId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "signatureId", "value": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001" },
    { "key": "binarySince", "value": "2020-01-01T00:00:00Z" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "_postman_id": "b2c3d4e5-f6a7-5b6c-9d0e-1f2a3b4c5d6e",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "_postman_id": "c3d4e5f6-a7b8-6c7d-0e1f-2a3b4c5d6e7f",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"newuser\",\n  \"password\": \"Test123!@#\",\n  \"email\": \"newuser@example.com\",\n  \"firstName\": \"New\",\n  \"lastName\": \"User\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "_postman_id": "d4e5f6a7-b8c9-7d8e-1f2a-3b4c5d6e7f8a",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.accessToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.accessToken);",
                  "if (j.refreshToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', j.refreshToken);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{username}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login as ADMIN",
          "_postman_id": "e5f6a7b8-c9d0-8e9f-2a3b-4c5d6e7f8a9b",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('username', 'admin');",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('password', 'Admin123!@#');"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.accessToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.accessToken);",
                  "if (j.refreshToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', j.refreshToken);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin123!@#\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login as USER",
          "_postman_id": "f6a7b8c9-d0e1-9f0a-3b4c-5d6e7f8a9b0c",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.accessToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.accessToken);",
                  "if (j.refreshToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', j.refreshToken);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"testuser\",\n  \"password\": \"Test123!@#\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh",
          "_postman_id": "a7b8c9d0-e1f2-0a1b-4c5d-6e7f8a9b0c1d",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.accessToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.accessToken);",
                  "if (j.refreshToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', j.refreshToken);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me",
          "_postman_id": "b8c9d0e1-f2a3-1b2c-5d6e-7f8a9b0c1d2e",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [ { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" } ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout (clear token)",
          "_postman_id": "c9d0e1f2-a3b4-2c3d-6e7f-8a9b0c1d2e3f",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', '');",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', '');"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Licenses",
      "_postman_id": "d0e1f2a3-b4c5-3d4e-7f8a-9b0c1d2e3f4a",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create License",
          "_postman_id": "e1f2a3b4-c5d6-4e5f-8a9b-0c1d2e3f4a5b",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.code) pm.collectionVariables.set('activationKey', j.code);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productId\": 1,\n  \"typeId\": 1,\n  \"ownerId\": 2,\n  \"deviceCount\": 2,\n  \"description\": \"Test license\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/licenses",
            "description": "Только ADMIN. В body не передавать id и code — их генерирует сервер. После ответа code сохраняется в переменную activationKey."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Activate License",
          "_postman_id": "f2a3b4c5-d6e7-5f6a-9b0c-1d2e3f4a5b6c",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"activationKey\": \"{{activationKey}}\",\n  \"deviceMac\": \"{{deviceMac}}\",\n  \"deviceName\": \"UserPC\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/licenses/activate"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Check License",
          "_postman_id": "a3b4c5d6-e7f8-6a7b-0c1d-2e3f4a5b6c7d",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"deviceMac\": \"{{deviceMac}}\",\n  \"productId\": {{productId}}\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/licenses/check"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Renew License",
          "_postman_id": "b4c5d6e7-f8a9-7b8c-1d2e-3f4a5b6c7d8e",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"activationKey\": \"{{activationKey}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/licenses/renew"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Signatures",
      "_postman_id": "e7f8a9b0-c1d2-8e9f-0a1b-2c3d4e5f6a7b",
      "description": "Сначала **Login as ADMIN** (в папке Auth), затем **Create signature** — после создания переменная signatureId подставится автоматически. Остальные запросы (Update, Delete, Get history, Get audit) используют этот id.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get full database",
          "_postman_id": "f8a9b0c1-d2e3-9f0a-1b2c-3d4e5f6a7b8c",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [ { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" } ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/signatures",
            "description": "Полная база — только ACTUAL. USER/ADMIN."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get increment",
          "_postman_id": "a9b0c1d2-e3f4-0a1b-2c3d-4e5f6a7b8c9d",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [ { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" } ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/signatures/increment?since=2020-01-01T00:00:00Z",
            "description": "Инкремент: записи с updatedAt > since (включая DELETED). Параметр since обязателен (ISO-8601)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get by IDs",
          "_postman_id": "b0c1d2e3-f4a5-1b2c-3d4e-5f6a7b8c9d0e",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"ids\": [\"{{signatureId}}\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/signatures/by-ids",
            "description": "Сигнатуры по списку UUID. Подставьте signatureId или несколько uuid в массив ids."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create signature",
          "_postman_id": "c1d2e3f4-a5b6-2c3d-4e5f-6a7b8c9d0e1f",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('signatureId', j.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"threatName\": \"Test.Malware\",\n  \"firstBytesHex\": \"4d5a\",\n  \"remainderHashHex\": \"e3b0c44298fc1c149afbf4c8996fb92427ae41e4649b934ca495991b7852b855\",\n  \"remainderLength\": 0,\n  \"fileType\": \"exe\",\n  \"offsetStart\": 0,\n  \"offsetEnd\": 2\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/signatures",
            "description": "Создание сигнатуры. Только ADMIN. После ответа id сохраняется в signatureId."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update signature",
          "_postman_id": "d2e3f4a5-b6c7-3d4e-5f6a-7b8c9d0e1f2a",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"threatName\": \"Test.Malware.Updated\",\n  \"firstBytesHex\": \"4d5a90\",\n  \"remainderHashHex\": \"e3b0c44298fc1c149afbf4c8996fb92427ae41e4649b934ca495991b7852b855\",\n  \"remainderLength\": 0,\n  \"fileType\": \"exe\",\n  \"offsetStart\": 0,\n  \"offsetEnd\": 3\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/signatures/{{signatureId}}",
            "description": "Обновление сигнатуры. Только ADMIN. Использует signatureId из переменной."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete signature",
          "_postman_id": "e3f4a5b6-c7d8-4e5f-6a7b-8c9d0e1f2a3b",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [ { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" } ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/signatures/{{signatureId}}",
            "description": "Логическое удаление (status = DELETED). Только ADMIN. 204 No Content."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get history",
          "_postman_id": "f4a5b6c7-d8e9-5f6a-7b8c-9d0e1f2a3b4c",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [ { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" } ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/signatures/{{signatureId}}/history",
            "description": "История версий по signatureId. Только ADMIN."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get audit",
          "_postman_id": "a5b6c7d8-e9f0-6a7b-8c9d-0e1f2a3b4c5d",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [ { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" } ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/signatures/{{signatureId}}/audit",
            "description": "Аудит действий по signatureId. Только ADMIN."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Signatures files",
      "_postman_id": "f0a1b2c3-d4e5-6f7a-8b9c-0d1e2f3a4b5c",
      "description": "Задание 6 (MinIO): только ADMIN. Сначала **Login as ADMIN**. Убедитесь, что MinIO запущен и заданы переменные приложения MINIO_* . В Upload выберите файл в поле **file** (form-data).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upload file (signature)",
          "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7a8b-9c0d-1e2f3a4b5c6d",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200 || pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  try { var j = pm.response.json(); if (j.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('signatureId', j.id); } catch (e) {}",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "file", "type": "file", "src": "" },
                { "key": "threatName", "type": "text", "value": "Sample.From.File", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/signatures/files/upload",
            "description": "multipart/form-data: поле **file** (обязательно). **threatName** — опционально (иначе из имени файла)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Presigned URLs by IDs",
          "_postman_id": "b2c3d4e5-f6a7-8b9c-0d1e-2f3a4b5c6d7e",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"ids\": [\"{{signatureId}}\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/signatures/files/presigned-urls",
            "description": "Список объектов { signatureId, presignedUrl }; URL null, если файла в хранилище нет."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Signatures binary",
      "_postman_id": "b6c7d8e9-f0a1-7b8c-9d0e-1f2a3b4c5d6e",
      "description": "Задание 5: бинарная выдача сигнатур. Ответ `200` с `Content-Type: multipart/mixed`: части **manifest.bin** и **data.bin** (application/octet-stream). Нужен Bearer-токен (USER или ADMIN).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET full (multipart/mixed)",
          "_postman_id": "c7d8e9f0-a1b2-8c9d-0e1f-2a3b4c5d6e7f",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "multipart/mixed,*/*" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/binary/signatures/full",
            "description": "Полная выгрузка только ACTUAL. Тело ответа — не JSON, а два бинарных файла в multipart."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET increment (multipart/mixed)",
          "_postman_id": "d8e9f0a1-b2c3-9d0e-1f2a-3b4c5d6e7f8a",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "multipart/mixed,*/*" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/binary/signatures/increment?since={{binarySince}}",
            "description": "Инкремент: записи с updatedAt > since (включая DELETED). Параметр since обязателен (ISO-8601). Меняйте переменную binarySince."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST by-ids (multipart/mixed)",
          "_postman_id": "e9f0a1b2-c3d4-0e1f-2a3b-4c5d6e7f8a9b",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "multipart/mixed,*/*" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"ids\": [\"{{signatureId}}\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/binary/signatures/by-ids",
            "description": "Бинарная выдача по списку UUID. Возвращаются только найденные записи."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
